    "headline": "The Campbell’s Company Declares Quarterly Dividend",
    "summary": "CAMDEN, N.J., May 13, 2026--The Board of Directors of The Campbell’s Company (NASDAQ:CPB) (Campbell’s) today declared a regular quarterly dividend on the company’s capital stock of $0.39 per share. The quarterly dividend is payable Aug. 3, 2026, to shareholders of record at the close of business as of July 2, 2026.",
